Author: Peter Rotich <peter@osticket.com>
Date:   Mon May 2 02:29:42 2016 +0000

    orm: Delegate ResultSet calls to QuerySet Iterator
    
    Allows for ability to access results without the need to call getIterator on
    the QuerySet. For example - $this->members->findFirst(array(...));
    
    This commit addresses regression issue brought about by commits 8ab4432f and
    eb0ba31 -- where ResultSet processing changed based on caching mode.

[33mcommit 35db37d4b6b31f679c4ee6b1f5379322c677de0e[m
Author: Jared Hancock <jared@osticket.com>
Date:   Thu Apr 28 10:34:09 2016 -0500

    cli: deploy: Don't remove the .MANIFEST or ost-config.php files

[33mcommit 934028253e4587ea4b0cd565a899f9b1c984853c[m
Author: Jared Hancock <jared@osticket.com>
Date:   Thu Apr 28 09:54:06 2016 -0500

    cli: deploy: Automatically deploy rewritten files
    
    With the advent of the MANIFEST file, files which are rewritten when
    deployed, such as those which have the GIT hash in the query string to force
    browser reloading, were no longer deployed unless the content of those files
    changed.
    
    This patch adds a flag to the MANIFEST file to indicate that the file was
    rewritten when it was deployed. This allows the file to be deployed and
    rewritten again when the deployment is run, but also adds an indication
    to the console output to distinguish deploying changes as opposed to
    deploying rewrites.

