[33mcommit 3263fae9d6c9b165946d4d068b9743680fe4bc4c[m
Merge: 31b05d57 b68a2363
Author: Peter Rotich <peter@rotich.com>
Date:   Thu Jun 20 09:16:41 2013 -0700

    Merge pull request #587 from greezybacon/issue/extensible-unpack
    
